about_the_game:
This bundle will unlock the &quot;Claudel Prairie&quot; area, created to resemble the vast world of &quot;Atelier Firis,&quot; and also will unlock some new character events for Firis.<br />
*This content unlocks after the final chapter of the game.<br />
*This content is also included in the &quot;Atelier Lydie &amp; Suelle Season Pass.&quot;

